<br>
The reason I came to think of this I recently had the problem of training the raid, because the monks were fd pulling 4 rooms away and still got hit by the mod rods, bringing aggro to me and the raid.<br>
<br>
Would 100-200 feet be more aproapriate? Bolts have an incredibly long range, and having ae rods be the same range is kinda extreme.<br>
<br>
And yes, I know, I learned and I don't do AE rods anymore =P<br>
I found it more mana efficiant to single the rods out, much like someone would ask for buffs, but still.. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=25288">Hobie Wan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
